  First-Pass Approval    ≥70%            Drafts approved without revision
  Rate                                   

  Revision Turnaround    ≤30 minutes     Time to fix blocked content

  Script Completion Rate 100%            Assigned scripts delivered

  Brand Voice            ≥90%            Spot-check audits
  Consistency                            
