# 7. ELECTRON-3 (Producer/Publisher) --- Complete Specification

## 7.1 Mission Statement

> **💡 ELECTRON-3\'S CORE PURPOSE**
>
> Transform approved scripts into premium video assets, run
> comprehensive QA checks, and execute safe publishing. Maintain
> technical excellence and complete audit trails for every piece of
> content.

## 7.2 Inputs

  ------------------ ------------------ ---------------------------------
  **Input**          **Source**         **Contains**

  Approved Creative  QUANTUM            Final script, storyboard, CTA,
                                        disclaimer

  Template Assets    Design system      Intros, outros, lower thirds,
                                        fonts

  Platform Specs     Platform           Aspect ratios, durations, file
                     documentation      formats

  Publishing         Operations         Scheduled times, platforms,
  Calendar                              tracking params

  Landing Pages      Marketing          URLs for CTAs, UTM parameters
  ------------------ ------------------ ---------------------------------

## 7.3 Outputs

  ------------------ ------------------------------ ---------------------
  **Output**         **Specification**              **Destination**

  Final Video        Platform-optimized, branded,   Publishing queue
                     subtitled                      

  Thumbnail/Cover    Branded, clickable, correct    Publishing queue
                     size                           

  Caption Package    Short + long versions,         Publishing queue
                     hashtags                       

  QA Report          Technical + Policy checklist   QUANTUM
                     results                        

  Publish Log        Timestamp, platform, post ID,  Audit database
                     asset hash                     
  ------------------ ------------------------------ ---------------------

## 7.4 Production Pipeline

1.  Receive approved creative package from QUANTUM

2.  Select appropriate AI video tool (see Section 10)

3.  Generate base video using script and storyboard

4.  Apply CorpFit template: intro, outro, lower thirds

5.  Add on-screen text with safe margins (readable on mobile)

6.  Generate or add subtitles (burned-in or platform captions)

7.  Audio cleanup: normalize volume, remove noise

8.  Export in all required platform formats

9.  Generate thumbnail/cover image

10. Run Technical QA checklist (see 7.5)

11. Run Policy QA checklist (see 7.6)

12. Verify all links and UTM parameters

13. Submit preview + QA report to QUANTUM

14. After approval: schedule post at designated time

15. Record publish log with all metadata

## 7.5 Technical QA Checklist

  ---------------- ------------------------------ -----------------------
  **Check**        **Requirement**                **Fail Action**

  Aspect Ratio     Matches platform (9:16, 16:9,  Re-export
                   1:1)                           

  Resolution       ≥1080p (1080x1920 for          Re-render
                   vertical)                      

  Text Sharpness   No blur, readable at any size  Adjust and re-export

  Safe Margins     Text not cut off on any device Reposition elements

  Audio Levels     Consistent, no clipping, -14   Re-normalize
                   LUFS                           

  Audio Quality    No harsh noise, clear speech   Re-process audio

  Logo Placement   Correct position per template  Fix and re-export

  Color Accuracy   Matches brand palette          Color correct

  File Size        Within platform limits         Optimize encoding

  Duration         Within platform limits         Trim or split
  ---------------- ------------------------------ -----------------------

## 7.6 Policy QA Checklist

  ---------------- ---------------------------------- --------------------
  **Check**        **Requirement**                    **Fail Action**

  Disclaimer       Required text visible if topic is  Add disclaimer
  Present          sensitive                          

  No Banned Claims Zero health/cure/guarantee         Return to ELECTRON-2
                   language                           

  Correct CTA      Matches brief, link works          Fix CTA

  Pricing Accurate If subscription content, pricing   Fix pricing
                   correct                            

  UTM Parameters   Tracking codes present and valid   Add/fix UTMs

  Landing Page     URL loads correctly                Fix or replace link
  ---------------- ---------------------------------- --------------------

**PART III: OPERATIONAL FRAMEWORK**

# 8. Handoff Contracts (Input/Output Specifications)

Each handoff between agents is a contract. If output doesn\'t match the
contract, QUANTUM blocks and returns.

  ------------- ----------------- ---------------------- -----------------
  **From → To** **Deliverable**   **Must Include**       **Reject If**

  E1 → QUANTUM  Trend Board (Top  Timestamp, source,     No sources, stale
                10-15)            funnel tag, module     trends, unmarked
                                  tag, risk label, 3     risks
                                  angles                 

  QUANTUM → E2  Production Brief  Platform, audience,    Missing
                                  module, CTA, do/don\'t funnel/module,
                                  constraints            unclear goal

  E2 → QUANTUM  Creative Package  Hook options, script,  Medical claims,
                                  storyboard, caption,   off-tone, vague
                                  CTA, disclaimer        content

  QUANTUM → E3  Approved Creative Final script,          Not approved,
                                  templates, platform    missing specs
                                  specs, publish         
                                  schedule               

  E3 → QUANTUM  Preview + QA      Rendered asset, tech   Failed QA,
                Report            QA, policy QA, link    missing logs
                                  verification           

  QUANTUM → E3  Publish Token     Approval ID, scheduled Any failed gate
                                  time, platform         
                                  confirmation           
  ------------- ----------------- ---------------------- -----------------

