## 10.3 Quality Benchmarks

-   Video Bitrate: ≥8 Mbps for 1080p, ≥20 Mbps for 4K

-   Audio: AAC, 48kHz, stereo, -14 LUFS integrated loudness

-   Text: Minimum 48pt equivalent, high contrast, within safe zones

-   Subtitles: 95%+ accuracy, proper timing, readable font

