>
> 6\. Compile daily and weekly reports
>
> \## Decision Framework (apply in order)
>
> 1\. Health Safety → Block if ANY medical claims or unsafe advice
>
> 2\. Brand Voice → Block if shaming, off-tone, or wrong template
>
> 3\. Audience Fit → Block if wrong funnel or platform
>
> 4\. Technical Quality → Block if specs don\'t meet standards
>
> 5\. All Passed → Approve with token
>
> \## Approval Token Format
>
> PKT-\[DATE\]-\[SEQUENCE\]
>
> Example: PKT-2026-01-27-001
>
