>
> \- decision: BLOCKED
>
> \- severity: \[CRITICAL/HIGH/MEDIUM\]
>
> \- reason: \[specific issue\]
>
> \- fix_instruction: \[exactly what to change\]
>
> \- return_to: \[ELECTRON-2 or ELECTRON-3\]
>
> \## Daily Report Format
>
> \- date: \[date\]
>
> \- content_produced: \[count by funnel/module\]
>
> \- content_approved: \[count\]
>
> \- content_blocked: \[count with reasons\]
>
> \- content_published: \[count by platform\]
>
> \- incidents: \[any policy violations\]
>
> \- tomorrow_priorities: \[top 3 focus areas\]

# Appendix C: Banned Phrases & Claims List

## C1. Absolute Bans (Never Use)

  --------------- -------------------------------------------------------
  **Category**    **Banned Phrases**

  Medical Claims  cure, treat, heal, fix, remedy, therapy, prescription,
                  diagnose, disease, condition

  Guarantees      guaranteed, proven, clinically proven, scientifically
                  proven, 100%, always works

  Weight Loss     lose X pounds, burn fat, melt away, shred, get skinny,
                  weight loss guaranteed

  Anti-Aging      reverse aging, anti-aging, turn back the clock, look
                  younger, age-defying

  Detox           detox, cleanse, flush toxins, purify, eliminate toxins

  Body Shaming    fat, skinny, ugly, gross, disgusting, shameful,
                  embarrassing

  Pressure        you must, you need to, you have to, you should, don\'t
                  be lazy
  --------------- -------------------------------------------------------

## C2. Caution Phrases (Use with Disclaimers)

  ---------------------- ------------------------------------------------
  **Phrase**             **Required Disclaimer**

  \"Research             Include source reference
  suggests\...\"         

  \"May help with\...\"  Add \"Results vary. Consult a professional.\"

  \"Some people          Include \"Individual experiences differ.\"
  find\...\"             

  \"Studies show\...\"   Cite the study or say \"some studies\"

  \"Can support\...\"    Frame as part of overall healthy lifestyle
  ---------------------- ------------------------------------------------

